Class Patch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tools.ant.ProjectComponent

        • org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.Patch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Patch
extends Task
    Patches a file by applying a 'diff' file to it; requires "patch" to be on the execution path.
    Since:
    Ant 1.1
